<item>
 <title>Episode 14 - BBC Radio Interview</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/xZKw51Lw5YI/episode+14+bbc+radio+interview</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;A quick update from Ian including our radio interview with the BBC&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
