<item>
 <title>Jake's Morning Power Smoothie</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/vwMQO_NIjiU/jakes+morning+power+smoothie</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;This smoothie is brilliant first thing and also can be made to be eaten/drank later, packed full of complex carbs, fibre, protien, some good simple sugars and healthy vits'n'mins!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 Fairtrade Mango&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 Fairtrade Banana&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;40g Cooked Oats&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 Scoop Unflavored Protien Powder&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Chop fruit and throw into smoothie maker (you can place them if your aim is a little shabby!) followed by your cooked oats and then the protien powder!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This will keep you full up for a good 3 hours when your next meal is due! A winner every time!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Protien powder-oats ratio can be changed according to your macronutrient needs!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=vwMQO_NIjiU:bo_f87gQC30:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=vwMQO_NIjiU:bo_f87gQC30:UT3xtbGYFzA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=UT3xtbGYFzA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=vwMQO_NIjiU:bo_f87gQC30:o5wlBzp-bFI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=o5wlBzp-bFI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description>
 <comments>http://www.smoothiecast.co.uk/smoothie+recipes/jakes+morning+power+smoothie#comments</comments>
