<item>
 <title>Grapezilla</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/57RAFSAKZsE/grapezilla</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;Need a pick up, this will have you buzzing all day long!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt; 2 Handfuls of Fairtrade green grapes &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; 2 Handfuls of Fairtrade red grapes &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; 250ml Grape juice &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; Juice of half a small Fairtrade lemon&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; 3 Scoops of frozen yoghurt &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Add all ingrediants to your smoothiemaker and you've got one ready to drink sugar rush!!! &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
