<item>
 <title>Amazing Grace</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/UKe9neJsTPY/amazing+grace</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;I have just got back from watching the new film 'Amazing Grace' about the abolition of the slave trade throughout the former British empire. I sobbed for much of the film, knowing what happened and the passion of the ones who fought to abolish the slave trade. But I cried even more  knowing that the slave trade was still going on today!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Every day people are bought and sold accross the world to work as slaves in the sex trade, in production of products and in food growth. I was really challenged by the film, and am asking my self "what can I do?". I'm not a member of parliament or a person with status... but I can make a difference! I can support the abolition of slavery, I can campaign and can buy the right things I can let others know and I can pray! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;How often do we turn a blind eye to what is going on, or buy the cheeper product? I know I do, when I can get three mangos for a quid instead of the fairtrade mango. I haven't lobbied my guts out to raise awareness of human trafficking. But why? because I can't be bothered, have other things to do, want more money for my self and overall I'm selfish. But if the radicals who abolished slavery had those attitudes I sometimes feel, there would be millions of Black people in slavery all around the world today still!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I want a change of heart daily, to stand up for what I know is right. By making noise about human trafficking, lobbying for change and buying Fairtrade wherever possible.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can join me in this wanting to change and start to make a huge impact on millions of lives and abolish slavery again and for good!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please visit this site, and lobby, and shout from rooftops, pray, do everything in your power to abolish the slave trade today!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.stopthetraffik.org" title="www.stopthetraffik.org"&gt;www.stopthetraffik.org&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=UKe9neJsTPY:JMD8UbmOHqU:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=UKe9neJsTPY:JMD8UbmOHqU:UT3xtbGYFzA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=UT3xtbGYFzA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=UKe9neJsTPY:JMD8UbmOHqU:o5wlBzp-bFI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=o5wlBzp-bFI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description>
