<item>
 <title>Fairtrade Clothing - M and S lead the way</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/D_GPi04di54/fairtrade+clothing+m+and+s+lead+way</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;We are all familiar with the various Fairtrade Products that are available; fruits, flowers, wine - there really is a good range available. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Also available are clothes that carry the Fairtrade mark - just another of the many areas that Fairtrade is branching into.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;!--break--&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Marks and Spencer (&lt;a href="http://www.marksandspencer.com" title="www.marksandspencer.com"&gt;www.marksandspencer.com&lt;/a&gt;) are a keen leader in this market and at the moment (Fairtrade Fortnight) they have a link on their homepage to their &lt;a href="http://www.marksandspencer.com/IWCatSectionView.process?IWAction=Load&amp;amp;Merchant_Id=1&amp;amp;Section_Id=9174&amp;amp;Page_Count=1&amp;amp;RestartFlow=t" title="Fairtrade Clothing"&gt;Fairtrade Section. &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;They've got a pretty good range on there, so pop on and have a look, see if you can find yourself some ethically traded clothes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And if M and S aren't your thing, they're not the only supplier of FT Clothing. Run a &lt;a href="http://www.google.co.uk/search?hl=en&amp;amp;client=firefox-a&amp;amp;rls=org.mozilla:en-GB:official&amp;amp;hs=u6j&amp;amp;sa=X&amp;amp;oi=spell&amp;amp;resnum=0&amp;amp;ct=result&amp;amp;cd=1&amp;amp;q=fair+trade+clothing&amp;amp;spell=1"&gt;google search&lt;/a&gt; and  see if you can find something more up your street.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Happy (Ethical!) Shopping!!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Andy&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=D_GPi04di54:bIraJMiFwMI:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=D_GPi04di54:bIraJMiFwMI:UT3xtbGYFzA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=UT3xtbGYFzA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=D_GPi04di54:bIraJMiFwMI:o5wlBzp-bFI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=o5wlBzp-bFI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
