<item>
 <title>Totally Fair: Port Ahoy</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/chXLD1aAQ8M/totally+fair+port+ahoy</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;One for the adults, don't have too many or you won't be able to see the port clearly, arrrgh!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A whole jar of Co-Op's Cranberry Sauce with port&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4 peeled, cored, stewed and then frozen Fairtrade Pears&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Add all ingredients to smoothie maker, hit go and your halfway to being a Fair-Pirate (if such a thing can exist). If you are of legal age and want to become a fully fledged pirate you can add a shot of Fairtrade white rum!!!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Remember to lobby your suppliers and grocers for more fairly traded products, then hopefully we will be able to add a shot of fairtrade port in the not to distant future!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Drink up me hearties yo ho !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
