 <title>Totally Fair: Ginger Rhupple Dip</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/mGRxNB9BuDc/totally+fair+ginger+rhupple+dip</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;A 'smoothie' with a nice kick, and its all fair!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt; 1 Jar of M&amp;amp;S Fairtrade Rhubarb and Ginger Conserve&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; 250ml Fairtrade Apple Juice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can add ice to make this into a true smoothie,  but I like to use it as a dip for Fairtrade Organic Brazil Nut Cookies, give it a go, you may discover your taste buds leaping for joy!!!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
