<item>
 <title>Totally Fair: Feeling Hedgey?</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/7kbD2hCWGCs/totally+fair+feeling+hedgey</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;If your feeling a little uneasy, this good ol' english hedgerow smoothie will calm you nicely!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A whole jar of M&amp;amp;S Fairtrade Hedgerow Conserve&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;500ml of Fairtrade Apple Juice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 handfuls of ice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All ingredients in head first (unless they are scared, go easy) Ice last! Hit smooth and sit back with a lovely calming and de-hedging smoothie!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=7kbD2hCWGCs:w5dbH-mXLp4:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=7kbD2hCWGCs:w5dbH-mXLp4:UT3xtbGYFzA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=UT3xtbGYFzA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=7kbD2hCWGCs:w5dbH-mXLp4:o5wlBzp-bFI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=o5wlBzp-bFI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
