 <title>Fairtrade fortnight at Newman</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/VLp5ADc5cJA/fairtrade+fortnight+newman</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;Today I (Jake) helped out at a Fairtrade stall in the Sanctuary (canteen) at Uni. We were selling loads of fairly traded food and giving out fairtrade fortune cookies (not really fortune cookies but had web address's on for fairtrade stuff, so better than any fortune cookie!). I didn't let people leave without taking a leaflet, there was quite literally a leaflet between them and the door! So much of newman has been dosed up on fairtrade, get in! and I got some nice fairtrade buntin to brighten my room and spread the fairtrade goodness!!!!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
