<item>
 <title>Totally Fair: Banana and Vanilla Yogshake</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/3x36nEXJ4e4/totally+fair+banana+and+vanilla+yogshake</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;An ace smoothie which is a fairtrade equivalent to your average milkshake!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 Fairtrade Vanilla Pod&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3 Fairtrade Bananas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 or 3 handfuls of ice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 pots of Fairtrade greek style yoghurt, from co-op&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4 teaspoons of fairtrade sugar dissolved in a small amount of water&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Slit vanilla pod lengthways and scrape out seeds, add bananas to smoothie maker follwed by yoghurt, sugar/water, vanilla seeds and then the ice. This is far better than any milkshke made with vanilla extract or essence etc. Fairtrade bananas and vanilla pods are top quality! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more details on where to buy fairtrade vanilla pods see:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;      &lt;a href="http://www.fairtrade.org.uk/products_spices_buy.htm" title="http://www.fairtrade.org.uk/products_spices_buy.htm"&gt;http://www.fairtrade.org.uk/products_spices_buy.htm&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=3x36nEXJ4e4:hYHG2wVs7yk:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=3x36nEXJ4e4:hYHG2wVs7yk:UT3xtbGYFzA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=UT3xtbGYFzA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=3x36nEXJ4e4:hYHG2wVs7yk:o5wlBzp-bFI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=o5wlBzp-bFI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description>
 <comments>http://www.smoothiecast.co.uk/smoothie+recipes/totally+fair+banana+and+vanilla+yogshake#comments</comments>
