<item>
 <title>Totally Fair: Apple and Blackcurrant</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/YpQI9eVDuRw/totally+fair+apple+and+blackcurrant</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;This is a very traditional flavoured smoothie, but with the ace twist that all the ingrediants used are giving people a fair price for their fruit!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;200ml Fruit passion apple juice from Co-Op&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Half a jar of blackcurrant conserve from M&amp;amp;S&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6 Fairtrade Grapes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handful of ice cubes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dead simple, all ingredients into the smoothiemaker, hit start and you've got yourself a totally fair Apple and Blackcurrant smoothie. Good thought old chap!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This recipe is only enough for one person so up the ingrediants if your smoothing for more than your self!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=YpQI9eVDuRw:5riuN2CAllA:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=YpQI9eVDuRw:5riuN2CAllA:UT3xtbGYFzA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=UT3xtbGYFzA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=YpQI9eVDuRw:5riuN2CAllA:o5wlBzp-bFI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=o5wlBzp-bFI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
