<item>
 <title>Totally Fair: The Zinger</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/_3nlq1-bu5w/totally+fair+zinger</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;Love a little zing in your life? Check this out!!!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1/2 Fairtrade Pineapple&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 Fairtrade Lemon&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 Fairtrade Clementines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handful of Fairtrade grapes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;150ml Fair Trade tropical juice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handful of ice cubes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Peel lemon, clementines and remove the outer nasty bits of pineapple, chop big fruits into peices and add all content to the smoothie maker (ice last)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This recipe is totally fairtrade (apart from the ice), Wohoooo!!!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=_3nlq1-bu5w:yZ3uzw6gxJo:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=_3nlq1-bu5w:yZ3uzw6gxJo:UT3xtbGYFzA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=UT3xtbGYFzA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=_3nlq1-bu5w:yZ3uzw6gxJo:o5wlBzp-bFI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=o5wlBzp-bFI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description>
