 <description>&lt;p&gt;Because I only had one lesson today, me and the charity team decided to prepare for Fairtrade Fortnight. We put up loads of posters around school, distributed leaflets, put a message in the school bulletin and made a big notice for the school plasma TVs! (picture below, sorry for poor quality, it's on my phone)&lt;br /&gt;
