<item>
 <title>Sunny Switzerland</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/Y-1gKVpgD5g/sunny+switzerland</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;Just got back from 10 days skiing in the swiss ski resort of Wengen, just under the famous north face of the Eiger. Had a great time and although the snow was a bit patchy the weather was mostly great. One of the highlights was hitting about 90 kmph down the Haneggschuss of the Lauberhorn Ski Race, although unfortunately the bindings on my skis gave way part way down and so I'm a bit bruised!! But it was great fun and I'd do it again, although hopefully with out the stop next time!!! I'm a big fan of skiing and had a great hol."&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;!--break--&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img src="http://www.smoothiecast.co.uk/files/lauberhorn.jpg" height="250" alt="skier"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
A skier coming down the Lauberhorn. Not me (obviously!)&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img src="http://www.smoothiecast.co.uk/files/wengen.jpg" height="200" alt="nice view"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
A nice view on a nice day. Round the corner to the right is the Schilthorn with a 360 degree rotating panorama restaurant.&lt;br /&gt;
A lot of the James Bond film 'On Her Majesty's Secret Service' was filmed up here and in the surrounding area.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
