 <title>Strawberry and Passionfruit Chill</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/MsW-tRxjDK8/strawberry+and+passionfruit+chill</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;This ice cool smoothie is sure to give you a refreshing chill&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handful of frozen Strawberries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 Banana&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;150ml Bio Yoghurt (Mango papaya and passionfruit is best)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;200ml Passionfruit Juice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;!--break--&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Mx in the smoothie maker until smooth, Serves 1-2&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
