<item>
 <title>Strawberries and Cream</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/rhfxbjA6W1s/strawberries+and+cream</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;For all you wimbledon fans out there!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 handfuls of strawberries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3 scoops of vanilla ice cream&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3 tablespoons of double cream&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handful of ice cubes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Wash and remove stalks on strawberries, then add all the lovely ingrediants to the smoothiemaker.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This smoothie isn't the one that springs to mind when you mention healthy, but remember we all need fat in moderation!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
