<item>
 <title>Crantastic</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/v-5HeM8lkTU/crantastic</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;Full of zest, a real 'pick me up'!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handful of cranberries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;250ml cranberry juice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handful of grapes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;400ml of natural yoghurt&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handful of ice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Prepare cranberries (remove stalks and wash), add all ingrediants to smoothiemaker- smooth, pour, drink, wake up!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This smoothie can be made without the cranberries, just add more juice to taste.&lt;br /&gt;
Grapes sweeten the smoothie but are not essential.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
