<item>
 <title>Melcumber Smoothie</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/mUDfub90Bp8/melcumber+smoothie</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;A lovely smoothie, not strictly a fruit smoothie but hey, nice all the same.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Half a small gala melon&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Half a small cucumber&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;250ml apple juice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handful of ice cubes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Remove outer skins from melon and cucumber, remove any seeds from melon, chop into small pieces and add all ingrediants to smoothie maker! Press smoothe! Enjoy!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=mUDfub90Bp8:d92b2KR877c:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=mUDfub90Bp8:d92b2KR877c:UT3xtbGYFzA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=UT3xtbGYFzA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=mUDfub90Bp8:d92b2KR877c:o5wlBzp-bFI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=o5wlBzp-bFI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
