<item>
 <title>Naughty Romance</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/d_zs4HWiRaM/naughty+romance</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;Naughty due to the chocolate, but nice to share with a loved one!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;50gms of Fairtrade white Chocolate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;250ml semi-skimmed milk&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7  large strawberries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Melt chocolate either in microwave or on the hob with half of the milk. When melted add the other half of the milk (already warmed), add milk/chocolate and strawberries to smoothie maker and your away. Serve this smoothie warm!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please ensure your smoothie maker is designed for warm smoothie making!!!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=d_zs4HWiRaM:vuP52_e3MsY:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=d_zs4HWiRaM:vuP52_e3MsY:UT3xtbGYFzA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=UT3xtbGYFzA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=d_zs4HWiRaM:vuP52_e3MsY:o5wlBzp-bFI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=o5wlBzp-bFI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description>
 <comments>http://www.smoothiecast.co.uk/smoothie+recipes/naughty+romance#comments</comments>
