<item>
 <title>Tangy Peach and Apricot</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/enjqIi34Tcc/tangy+peach+and+apricot</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;To make this tangy smoothie you will need:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 Large peach&lt;/li&gt;
