<item>
 <title>Smoothies For Athletes</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/QGM13dxAbIw/smoothies+athletes</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;The Smoothies for athletes eBook has 126 recipes and information about the health benefits of smoothies. All the recipes have a thorough description and include all the nutritional info such as calories, carbs, sugar and protein. The ebook contains recipes including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Double Melon&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quad Berry Quencher&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Vitamin Cups Smoothie, and many more healthy recipes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This ebook is a must have for any athletes, the information will help improve your diet and training programme.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
