<item>
 <title>The Fairtrade Mark</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/-TD6EwwdfUI/fairtrade+mark</link>
 <description>&lt;h3&gt;What does it mean when you see the Fairtrade logo?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Farmers get a fair and stable price for their products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Farmers and plantation workers get extra income to improve their lives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A greater respect for the environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Small farmers have stronger position in world markets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A closer link between you and the producers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;!--break--&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img src="/files/mark_colour_horizontal.JPG" alt="Fairtrade Mark" align="center" width="100%" style="max-width:642px;"/&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Next time you go shopping, stop and think about where the product comes from. Did the farmer get a fair deal? The fairtrade mark guarantees this. Change today, choose Fairtrade! &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=-TD6EwwdfUI:zGSoEiz5IDQ:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=-TD6EwwdfUI:zGSoEiz5IDQ:UT3xtbGYFzA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=UT3xtbGYFzA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=-TD6EwwdfUI:zGSoEiz5IDQ:o5wlBzp-bFI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=o5wlBzp-bFI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description>
 <comments>http://www.smoothiecast.co.uk/fairtrade/fairtrade+mark#comments</comments>
