<item>
 <title>Fruitily Fair Plum and Avocado </title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/BToOY7EoNMM/fruitily+fair+plum+and+avocado</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;For this delicious smoothie full of fairtrade goodness you will need:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4 fair trade plums&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 fair trade avocado&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handful of fair trade white grapes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;250ml fairtrade orange juice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handful of ice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Peel and de-stone the plums, slice the avocado in half, remove the pit, and scoop out the flesh. Add all ingredients to smoothie maker and mix until smooth&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Serves 3-4&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=BToOY7EoNMM:7TkicoT0rEk:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=BToOY7EoNMM:7TkicoT0rEk:UT3xtbGYFzA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=UT3xtbGYFzA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=BToOY7EoNMM:7TkicoT0rEk:o5wlBzp-bFI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=o5wlBzp-bFI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description>
