<item>
 <title>Guava, Passionfruit and Mango</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/yGDmrbaXNGE/guava+passionfruit+and+mango</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;For this zingy and aromatic smoothie you will need:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 fairtrade mango&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 guavas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;300ml passion fruit juice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 handfuls of ice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Chop guava into chunks, cut mango flesh away from stone and add all ingredients to smoothie maker and hit smooth! Serves 3-4&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=yGDmrbaXNGE:EmFIqT7Kz8o:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=yGDmrbaXNGE:EmFIqT7Kz8o:UT3xtbGYFzA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=UT3xtbGYFzA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=yGDmrbaXNGE:EmFIqT7Kz8o:o5wlBzp-bFI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=o5wlBzp-bFI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
