<item>
 <title>Limey Melon Smoothie</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/s--6nl9Wz-Y/limey+melon+smoothie</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;For the limey melon smoothie, you will need:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 1/2 cups watermelon&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 1/2 cups honeydew melon&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 limes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 cup vanilla lowfat yoghurt &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 cup ice cubes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1 cup = about a quarter of the final amount of smoothie&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Slice the melons and remove the skin. Squeeze the limes to get the juice out of them. Pour in the yoghurt and ice cubes. Blend until smooth. Serves 4!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=s--6nl9Wz-Y:4_1tgNf89E0:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=s--6nl9Wz-Y:4_1tgNf89E0:UT3xtbGYFzA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=UT3xtbGYFzA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=s--6nl9Wz-Y:4_1tgNf89E0:o5wlBzp-bFI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=o5wlBzp-bFI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description>
 <comments>http://www.smoothiecast.co.uk/smoothie+recipes/limey+melon+smoothie#comments</comments>
