<item>
 <title>Papaya and Raspberry Smoothie</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/4qdThNpYTY8/papaya+and+raspberry+smoothie</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;Ingredients for the papaya and rasberry smoothie:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 frozen banana, peeled &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1/2 fresh papaya &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10-12 raspberries (fresh or frozen) &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;300ml Fruit Juice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pour all ingredients into smoothie maker, then whizz until smoothie consistency is reached&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=4qdThNpYTY8:o0KlK6jiugk:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=4qdThNpYTY8:o0KlK6jiugk:UT3xtbGYFzA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=UT3xtbGYFzA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=4qdThNpYTY8:o0KlK6jiugk:o5wlBzp-bFI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=o5wlBzp-bFI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description>
