<item>
 <title>Tropical Five Fruit Smoothie</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/BBjydOtPmc8/tropical+five+fruit+smoothie</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;This super fruity smoothie will give you your five a day all in one if you're feeling hungry, also great for sharing with a friend. You will need:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 large fairtrade banana &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 kiwi fruit &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1/2 medium fairtrade mango &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1/2 medium&amp;nbsp; papaya &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;300ml fairtrade orange juice &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3-5 ice cubes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Peel and chop up the banana, peel and quarter the kiwis, peel and dice the papaya and mango. Add all the ingredients to the smoothiemaker and pour in the orange juice and ice cubes. Whizz until smooth. Serves 1-2.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=BBjydOtPmc8:kk1aRv2ahk8:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=BBjydOtPmc8:kk1aRv2ahk8:UT3xtbGYFzA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=UT3xtbGYFzA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=BBjydOtPmc8:kk1aRv2ahk8:o5wlBzp-bFI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=o5wlBzp-bFI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description>
 <comments>http://www.smoothiecast.co.uk/smoothie+recipes/tropical+five+fruit+smoothie#comments</comments>
