<item>
 <title>Asian Pear and Papaya</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/qyfOWm7Cdvs/asian+pear+and+papaya</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;To make the Asian Pear smoothie you will need:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 Asian / Chinese Pear&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 Papayas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1/2 of a Fair Trade Mango&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3/4 Japanese Fuji (optional)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;300ml Fair Trade tropical juice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handful of ice cubes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cut the asian pear into segments, scoop out the papaya flesh, cut off half of the mango and slice up the fuji and put them into the smoothie maker. Add the tropical juice and ice. Then whizz!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=qyfOWm7Cdvs:4Aq_4TIBhAI:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=qyfOWm7Cdvs:4Aq_4TIBhAI:UT3xtbGYFzA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=UT3xtbGYFzA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=qyfOWm7Cdvs:4Aq_4TIBhAI:o5wlBzp-bFI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=o5wlBzp-bFI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description>
