<item>
 <title>Oriental Splash</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/Q5ADgfAKKsk/oriental+splash</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;Here's the recipe for this week's oriental splash smoothie: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3 mandarins&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 lychee&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handful of Ice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Peel and chop up the mandarins, chop up the lychee and and grab a handful of ice cubes from the freezer, put all the ingredients in the smoothie maker and then blend until smooth! If your smoothie maker is struggling try adding some juice to smoothen it up&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=Q5ADgfAKKsk:_uFzSDpHJLU:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=Q5ADgfAKKsk:_uFzSDpHJLU:UT3xtbGYFzA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=UT3xtbGYFzA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=Q5ADgfAKKsk:_uFzSDpHJLU:o5wlBzp-bFI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=o5wlBzp-bFI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
