<item>
 <title>Fairtrade Ginger and Vanilla</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/xsUvahL1xCg/fairtrade+ginger+and+vanilla</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;For this fairtrade ginger and vanilla smoothie you will need:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 Fairtrade bananas
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 tbs Fairtrade vanilla extract
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 tsp Ginger spice blend
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;500 ml Yoghurt
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handful of Ice cubes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As usual put all the ingredients in the smoothie maker and blend until you have reached smoothie consistency&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=xsUvahL1xCg:BL39J3E4GMo:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=xsUvahL1xCg:BL39J3E4GMo:UT3xtbGYFzA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=UT3xtbGYFzA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=xsUvahL1xCg:BL39J3E4GMo:o5wlBzp-bFI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=o5wlBzp-bFI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
