<item>
 <title>Fairtrade Tropical Banana and Honey</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/T0Ha1iN4iVo/fairtrade+tropical+banana+and+honey</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;To make this delicious fruit smoothie you will need... &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;300ml tropical juice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3 small or 2 large bananas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 tablespoon of honey&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6 ice cubes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Note: All these ingredients are available as fairtrade so please make sure you use fairtrade products and make a differece!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Put the ingredients in your smoothie maker and make it whizz. It shouldn't take long to make this one because there isn't much ice. When the ice stops crackling turn it off and pour out. It should have fairly thick smoothie consistency.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=T0Ha1iN4iVo:Qq9-kZBBv88:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=T0Ha1iN4iVo:Qq9-kZBBv88:UT3xtbGYFzA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=UT3xtbGYFzA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=T0Ha1iN4iVo:Qq9-kZBBv88:o5wlBzp-bFI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=o5wlBzp-bFI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description>
 <comments>http://www.smoothiecast.co.uk/smoothie+recipes/fairtrade+tropical+banana+and+honey#comments</comments>
