<item>
 <title>Strawberry and banana</title>
 <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/smoothiecast/~3/mItjxV0unbg/strawberry+and+banana</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;This smoothie is officially tastier than the top pre-made smoothies as tested in Episode 8. Make it yourself by using:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 large banana&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;13 strawberries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 handful of grapes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1/2 cup of apple juice (or an apple and some water)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 Handful of icecubes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Prepare fruits as normal. Mix until you reach smoothie consistency&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experiment, be creative, change the quantities around or even add new ingredients to find your favourite strawberry and banana smoothie.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=mItjxV0unbg:sawVw_uiM9c:yIl2AUoC8zA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=mItjxV0unbg:sawVw_uiM9c:UT3xtbGYFzA"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=UT3xtbGYFzA" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?a=mItjxV0unbg:sawVw_uiM9c:o5wlBzp-bFI"&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/smoothiecast?d=o5wlBzp-bFI" border="0"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description>
